Package: go-dbadmin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, mysql-client | mysql-client-8.0 | default-mysql-client
Description: Modern web-based MySQL administration tool (GoDBAdmin)
 A beautiful and fast web-based MySQL database administration tool
 built with Go and React. Provides an intuitive interface for managing
 MySQL databases, executing queries, and viewing table data.
 .
 Features:
  - Modern, responsive web interface with dark mode
  - Fast query execution with connection pooling
  - Database and table browser with tree view
  - SQL query editor with syntax highlighting (Monaco Editor)
  - Table structure viewer
  - Paginated data viewing
  - JWT-based authentication
  - Support for multiple MySQL connections
